# packages/engine — the product (pure-function Python)
#
# Submodules (added in Phase 1):
#   regimes.py, profiles.py, types.py
#   market_state/, flow_score/, strike_selector/, recommendation/, decision/
#   confidence/, execution/, outcomes/
#   collar_builder/        (v1.1 — first-class engine)
#   scoring/               (v1.1 — iv, structure, gamma, event)
#   payoff/, scenarios/, providers/
#   config/                (weights.yaml, rules.yaml)
#
# Invariant: NO I/O. NO DB. NO NETWORK. Pure functions only.
# The API layer (apps/api) hydrates inputs and persists outputs.
